{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·007.1", "text_original": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于穀，無啄我粟。\n此邦之人，不我肯穀。言旋言歸，復我邦族。", "text_normalized": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于穀，無啄我粟。\n此邦之人，不我肯穀。言旋言歸，復我邦族。", "notes": "黃鳥 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·007.2", "text_original": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于桑，無啄我粱。\n此邦之人，不可與明。言旋言歸，復我諸兄。", "text_normalized": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于桑，無啄我粱。\n此邦之人，不可與明。言旋言歸，復我諸兄。", "notes": "黃鳥 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·007.3", "text_original": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于栩，無啄我黍。\n此邦之人，不可與處。言旋言歸，復我諸父。", "text_normalized": "黃鳥黃鳥，無集于栩，無啄我黍。\n此邦之人，不可與處。言旋言歸，復我諸父。", "notes": "黃鳥 Chinese stanza 3."}
